|x-1|<{1\over4} \Longleftrightarrow -{1\over4} < x - 1 < {1\over4} \Longleftrightarrow {1\over2} < 2x-1 < {3\over2}
|x-1|\lt \frac{1}{4}
-\frac{1}{4}\lt x-1
\frac{3}{4}\lt x
2x-1\gt \frac{1}{2}
|2x-1|\gt \frac{1}{2}
|2x-1|\ge \frac{1}{2}
